---
title: Easy Sri Lankan Chicken & Roast Veggie Salad with Garlic Yoghurt
description: If we had to list our favourite things about Sri Lankan food, we’d be here all night. But one of the best things is
the variety of exciting vegetables used in every dish! Tonight's dinner is no exception with a rainbow of roasted
veggies, tossed together with leafy greens and topped by mildly spiced chicken. With a speedy prep time,
you'll have this warm and comforting meal gobbled down in no time at all.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*Keep an eye out... Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced cauliflower with capsicum, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
